{"root":{"data":{"id":"davkrqx3ao80","created":1750850689634,"text":"mesa-3d"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"davks0qel0g0","created":1750850710998,"text":"opengl"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlslbn54g0","created":1750853576927,"text":"opengles"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davksmg84m80","created":1750850758271,"text":"vulkan"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlsrj60800","created":1750853590443,"text":"egl"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlssxqllk0","created":1750853593501,"text":"openmax"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlt31bvpc0","created":1750853615486,"text":"opencl"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlt706zwg0","created":1750853624124,"text":"vdpau"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davlt8sre000","created":1750853628028,"text":"va-api"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davkspvsbhs0","created":1750850765743,"text":"drm","note":"DRM（直接渲染管理）：\nLinux内核用于管理显卡硬件的子系统，防止用户直接操作显卡硬件导致系统死机。支持多客户端调用\n\n\nlibdrm：\n用户态接口库，属于很低层级的库，常被一些图形驱动调用，例如Mesa-DRI驱动，X-Server驱动，libav等类似项目"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davkvoj5zyw0","created":1750850997895,"text":"dri"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"davl3pug1dk0","created":1750851627667,"text":"GLU/GLUT","note":"GLU：\n基于GL（opengl）的API，封装的一层工具函数，简化常用开发方法\n\nGLUT：\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbdchg15a6g0","created":1752655392634,"text":"GLX","note":"作为x server的一个扩展存在，用于x11调用OpenGL接口的能力。GLX是在X11上用于提供OpenGL与窗口交互、窗口管理等等的一组API。它的作用与Windows的WGL、Mac OS X的AGL以及针对OpenGL ES的EGL相似。在Linux上，窗口创建、管理等API遵循X Window接口，而GLX提供了OpenGL与X Window交互的办法"},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}